When we went to report ourselves
being alive to Headquarters,

55
00:08:18,748 --> 00:08:20,083
we heard about you.

56
00:08:21,150 --> 00:08:24,954
We left Allied Forces Camp
right away and I came here,

57
00:08:25,955 --> 00:08:27,624
while Captain went to Albania.

58
00:08:28,157 --> 00:08:29,792
What happened to you two?

59
00:08:30,994 --> 00:08:33,730
You and Si Jin...

60
00:08:34,464 --> 00:08:37,033
You were soldiers killed in combat by a bomb
attack with bodies that were unrecoverable.

61
00:08:45,041 --> 00:08:47,377
The militia were one foot
faster than the bomb attack.

62
00:08:49,000 --> 00:08:51,414
Before the bomb attack, we
were dragged to a dugout.

63
00:08:52,770 --> 00:08:54,951
We were locked up in that
unknown underground place,

64
00:08:56,070 --> 00:09:00,356
and on approximately the
150th or 155th day...

65
00:09:09,940 --> 00:09:13,036
Finish both and we're pulling out.
Hurry.

66
00:09:24,147 --> 00:09:28,284
I will pay you back for the cookie
even if it's in the afterlife.

67
00:09:30,150 --> 00:09:32,288
This is the payment for
the cookie I owed you.

68
00:09:33,456 --> 00:09:34,691
I wish you luck.

69
00:09:35,091 --> 00:09:37,393
I got the help of a friend

70
00:09:38,750 --> 00:09:40,330
from that faraway place.

71
00:09:42,570 --> 00:09:43,666
It's all set.

72
00:09:44,650 --> 00:09:46,469
How did you know to come
with a broken arm again?

73
